On Fri, 2005-05-20 09:48:35 -0400, Richard B. Johnson <linux-os@analogic.com> wrote:
>     len = getpagesize();
>     if((fd = open("/dev/mem", O_RDWR)) == FAIL)
>         ERRORS("open");
>     if((sp = mmap((void *)SCREEN, len, PROT, TYPE, fd, SCREEN))==MAP_FAILED)
